PARKER v. STATE [App. No. 43,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided March 5, 1965.

Before Hammond, Horney, Marbury, Sybert, OppEnheimer and Barnes, JJ.

*655Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Powers in the court below.

Application denied.
